[{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0007","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-2744","title":"Chyrp Chyrp 2.0/2.1 路径遍历漏洞","description":"Chyrp 2.1 及更早版本（含 2.0）在默认 URI 的请求处理中存在目录遍历（CWE-22）漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需在请求默认 URI 时于 action 参数中构造并传入经 URL 编码的 `..%2F`（即编码后的点点斜杠）序列，即可突破程序预期的路径限制，使应用程序包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞属于典型的本地文件包含（LFI）类问题，攻击者借此可读取到本不应暴露的敏感文件（如配置文件、源码等），进而可能获取系统凭据或进一步推进攻击。其触发条件简单，仅需向目标站点发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级为中高危，主要影响部署了相关版本 Chyrp 博客系统的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2011-2744"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-07-19T20:55:01.257","updated":"2026-06-16T23:31:54.793","remediation":"升级 Chyrp 到官方修复版本（2.1 之后的 2.x 版本，建议查阅项目仓库获取含路径遍历修复的提交）；若无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）配置中拦截向默认 URI 传入含 ..%2F 编码序列的 action 参数请求，并限制 PHP 仅可包含白名单目录内文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/73890","http://secunia.com/advisories/45184","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8312","http://www.justanotherhacker.com/advisories/JAHx113.txt","http://www.ocert.org/advisories/ocert-2011-001.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/5","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2011/07/13/6","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/518890/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/48672","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/68564","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/35945","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-2744.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-2744.js","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/medium/CVE-2011-2780.yaml","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/8b3d6ccb0f4e9e36a888697a7de582054e8c5bc9/2011/CVE-2011-2744.json","https://github.com/kaismax/CVE-Poc/blob/6d8c93dabf674cea102713781cc534d577412357/2011/CVE-2011-2744.md","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2011-2744-2047.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2011-2744-2048.yaml","https://github.com/PwnAwan/CVEs/blob/967839a1f3dd2e43c3ca7af98749ae1712e69a04/2011/CVE-2011-2780.md","https://github.com/Ciyfly/woodpecker/blob/f88bed6da55238547a423ce17dccb2cdbc93be50/pocs/nuclei/cves/2011/CVE-2011-2744.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0006","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-2523","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9148,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10837}}","description":"vsftpd 2.3.4 版本在 2011 年 6 月 30 日至 7 月 3 日期间被植入恶意后门，该后门会在目标主机上监听 6200/tcp 端口并开放一个 root 权限的 shell。攻击者只需向 FTP 服务的登录用户名中注入特定笑脸字符 \":)\" 即可触发后门，在未授权的情况下远程执行任意命令，导致服务器被完全控制。该漏洞影响在此期间下载安装的 vsftpd 2.3.4 版本，CVSS 评分为 9.8（严重），任何能够访问目标 FTP 服务及其 6200 端口的网络攻击者均可利用此漏洞获取系统最高权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2011-2523"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2019-11-27T21:15:12.387","updated":"2026-06-16T23:31:30.717","remediation":"建议立即升级 vsftpd 至 2.3.5 或更高版本（官方已发布修复版本）。若暂时无法升级，请在防火墙层面封禁 6200/tcp 端口防止后门连接，并检查系统是否已被植入恶意代码。同时建议从官方站点 https://security.appspot.com/vsftpd.html 重新下载验证过的源码包编译安装，避免使用 2011年6月30日至7月3日期间下载的被篡改版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.com/files/162145/vsftpd-2.3.4-Backdoor-Command-Execution.html","https://access.redhat.com/security/cve/cve-2011-2523","https://packetstormsecurity.