"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0005","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-1669","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16370,\"outputTokens\":32,\"totalTokens\":16402}}","description":"Mikoviny WP Custom Pages 模块（WordPress 插件，版本 0.5.0.1）的 wp-download.php 文件存在目录遍历（路径遍历）漏洞，属于 CWE-22 类型。该脚本在处理用户传入的 `url` 参数时未对路径进行充分校验与规范化，远程攻击者可在 `url` 参数中插入经过 URL 编码的 `..%2F`（即编码后的\"点点斜杠\"）序列，借此跨越 Web 根目录限制并读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源码或敏感系统文件）。该漏洞影响所有安装并使用此插件 0.5.0.1 版本的 WordPress 站点，利用条件仅需攻击者能够网络访问目标站点的 wp-download.php 接口，无需身份认证，通过构造恶意 HTTP 请求即可实现任意文件读取。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-1669"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-04-10T02:51:20.167","updated":"2026-06-16T23:29:47.217","remediation":"建议立即升级 WordPress 插件 WP Custom Pages 至 0.5.0.2 或更高版本（官方已修复该目录遍历漏洞）。如暂时无法升级，可通过 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）或 Nginx/Apache 配置规则拦截包含 `..%2F` 或 `../` 等路径遍历序列的 `url` 参数请求，或临时禁用该插件的 `wp-download.php` 文件访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/71707","http://secunia.com/advisories/43963","http://www.autosectools.com/Advisories/WordPress.WP.Custom.Pages.0.5.0.1_Local.File.Inclusion_169.html","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17119","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/47146","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/66559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17119","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-1669.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-1669.js","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/c8e5b5fa7d3cc58de338ca5a0a33eeafcde1afac/CVE-2011/CVE-2011-16xx/CVE-2011-1669.json","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2011/CVE-2011-1669.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-1669_19.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2011-1669-2045.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder4/cve-2011-1669-2041.yaml","https://github.com/thompson005/nuclei-scanner/blob/6b5cfd844640c882a3d278f76f395a74ee14ef81/nucleivault/new%20templates/CVE-2011-1669-2041.yaml","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/CVE-2011-1669.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0004","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0762","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9205,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10893}}","description":"vsftpd 2.3.3 之前版本的 ls.c 文件中的 vsf_filename_passes_filter 函数存在拒绝服务漏洞。经过身份认证的远程攻击者可在多个 FTP 会话中通过 STAT 命令发送精心构造的 glob 通配符表达式（如复杂的嵌套匹配模式）触发该漏洞，导致服务器 CPU 资源被大量消耗并耗尽进程槽位，最终造成服务拒绝。该漏洞属于资源不受控制的消耗（CWE-400）类型，攻击条件要求攻击者拥有有效的 FTP 登录凭证，CVSS 评分 4.0，危害等级中等。此漏洞与 CVE-2010-2632 为不同的缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0762"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-03-02T20:00:01.770","updated":"2026-06-16T23:28:01.427","remediation":"建议立即升级 vsftpd 到 2.3.3 或更高版本（如 3.0.3 等稳定版），以修复 vsf_filename_passes_filter 函数中的 glob 表达式拒绝服务漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可在 FTP 服务器配置中限制单用户最大并发会话数（如 max_per_ip=2、max_clients=50），并在防火墙层面限制单 IP 并发 FTP 连接数，缓解 CPU 耗尽与进程槽耗尽风险。建议同时监控 FTP 服务进程数与 CPU 占用，异常时自动重启服务或封禁异常 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=622741","http://cxib.net/stuff/vspoc232.c","http://jvn.jp/en/jp/JVN37417423/index.html","http://lists.fedoraproject.org/pipermail/package-announce/2011-March/055881.html","http://lists.fedoraproject.org/pipermail/package-announce/2011-March/055882.html","http://lists.fedoraproject.org/pipermail/package-announce/2011-March/055957.html","http://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-security-announce/2011-05/msg00005.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=133226187115472&w=2","http://securityreason.com/achievement_securityalert/95","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8109","http://www.debian.org/security/2011/dsa-2305","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16270","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/590604","http://www.mandriva.com/security/advisories?name=MDVSA-2011:049","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2011-0337.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/516748/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/46617","http://www.securitytracker.com/id?1025186","http://www.ubuntu.com/usn/USN-1098-1","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0547","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0639","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0668","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0713","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/65873","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16270","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0762.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-0762.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/e0c5bd1f60d27097ef70e1e950114a7212279c8f/2011/CVE-2011-0762.json","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/network/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0762.yaml","https://github.com/arschlochnop/VulnWatchdog/blob/b19933d8753463987b80b588cdb9781b0e8db158/data/2011/CVE-2011-0762-Andreyfrtz_CVE-2011-0762.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2011/CVE-2011-0762","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-0762_1.yaml","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2011/CVE-2011-0762.md","https://github.com/eslerm/ubuntu-cve-tracker/blob/f17e5ebf7a87347cc68d8fae347d07409a857342/retired/CVE-2011-0762","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/gb_mandriva_MDVSA_2011_049.nasl","https://github.com/s3mPr1linux/CVE-2011-0762"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0003","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0518","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16355,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":16383}}","description":"LotusCMS Fraise 3.0 版本的 core/lib/router.php 文件存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞。当服务器关闭 magic_quotes_gpc 安全配置时，未经过身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 发送带有特制 system 参数的 HTTP 请求，绕过路径限制读取并包含服务器上的任意本地文件。攻击者可借此查看敏感文件内容，甚至通过包含含恶意代码的文件实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 LotusCMS Fraise 3.0 版本，CVSS 评分为 5.1，危害等级为中危，利用前提为目标系统未启用 magic_quotes_gpc 且可直接访问 Web 服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0518"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-01-20T19:00:12.333","updated":"2026-06-16T23:27:32.930","remediation":"建议升级 LotusCMS Fraise 至 3.0.1 或更高版本（已修复该目录遍历漏洞），或迁移至维护中的 CMS。临时缓解：在 php.ini 中开启 magic_quotes_gpc=On（PHP 5.4+ 已移除），或设置 open_basedir 限制文件访问范围，同时设置 allow_url_include=Off 禁用远程文件包含。建议升级 PHP 至 5.4+ 版本以移除 magic_quotes_gpc 依赖并启用 open_basedir 限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/70409","http://secunia.com/advisories/42835","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15964","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0073","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/64736","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/15964","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e7bd0957d7eea7c21095268cca9721e428611ed/cves/2011/0xxx/CVE-2011-0518.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2011/CVE-2011-0518","https://github.com/b1ank1108/VulSentinel/blob/12fae384c4fef6ba595f65eae09dc323d97a95f4/reports/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/masahiro331/nvd-list/blob/4937ab886b2d99e2047bc7eafc242f2653ee7558/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra","https://github.com/rojo32/python/blob/2af471c8b7440b4c4dfa80f54c96eb69c3a465ee/Proyecto_Scrapy/vulneravilidades/vulneravilidades/spiders/vulnerabilidades.csv","https://github.com/Kuduxaaa/hunting-knowledge-base/blob/e9de2ea715300eb67318e21f3930704d36ad8d2b/signatures/nuclei/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0518.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/bf9978ea592b7413bb96dfeb9db92cbd52bf0c3d/api/2011/CVE-2011-0518.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0002","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-0049","title":"Majordomo Majordomo 2 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Majordomo 2 在 20110131 之前的版本中，lib/Majordomo.pm 文件的 _list_file_get 函数存在目录遍历漏洞。由于该函数未对用户输入中的文件路径进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可借助 help 命令中携带的\"..\"（点点）路径序列读取服务器上的任意文件。攻击条件为：攻击者无需身份认证，可通过发送特制的电子邮件，或经由 Web 接口中的 cgi-bin/mj_wwwusr 页面提交恶意请求来触发该漏洞。受影响范围为 Majordomo 2 早于 20110131 的所有版本，可能造成敏感文件（如配置文件、口令文件等）泄露，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2011-0049"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2011-02-04T01:00:07.400","updated":"2026-06-16T23:26:41.687","remediation":"升级 Majordomo 至 2011-01-31 及之后版本（Majordomo 2.0 及以上修复版），从官方源码仓库获取并重新部署 lib/Majordomo.pm。如暂时无法升级，应限制 cgi-bin/mj_wwwusr 网络接口的访问来源（如 Web 服务器 ACL 或防火墙仅允许可信 IP），并禁用或过滤 help 命令中传入的“../”路径遍历字符，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/70762","http://secunia.com/advisories/43125","http://securityreason.com/securityalert/8061","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16103","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/363726","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/516150/100/0/threaded","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/46127","http://www.securitytracker.com/id?1025024","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2011/0288","https://bug628064.bugzilla.mozilla.org/attachment.cgi?id=506481","https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=628064","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/65113","https://sitewat.ch/en/Advisory/View/1","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2011/CVE-2011-0049.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2011/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2011-0049-2040.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2011-0049.js","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2011/CVE-2011-0049/poc/nuclei/CVE-2011-0049.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2011-0049_4.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2011-0049-2036.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2011-0049-2036.yaml","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/ad98898aca7860353055ea2aee0af12336215af4/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/jas502n/nmap-zh/blob/968f1f4ccb968c214ca1fa0414ba5023c9345ec2/nmap-7.70/scripts/http-majordomo2-dir-traversal.nse"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2011-0001","file_name":"2011/AVE-2011-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2011-10043","title":"Perl Module::Load 任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Perl 的 Module::Load 模块在 0.22 版本之前存在路径校验缺陷，当加载的模块名称以 \"::\" 开头时，可绕过 @INC 安全限制加载任意路径的 Perl 模块。攻击者若能控制传递给 load 函数的模块名参数，即可利用此漏洞加载恶意模块并执行任意代码。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重，影响所有使用受影响版本 Module::Load 的 Perl 应用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-2011-10043"],"sources":["cnnvd"],"published":"2026-07-07T12:16:24.880","updated":"2026-07-07T17:16:31.890","remediation":"立即将 Perl 的 Module::Load 模块升级至 0.22 或更高版本。在升级不可行时，对传递给 load 函数的模块名进行校验，拒绝以 \"::\" 开头的字符串。同时审查调用链，确保用户输入不会直接或间接影响模块名参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://blogs.perl.org/users/michael_g_schwern/2011/10/how-not-to-load-a-module-or-bad-interfaces-make-good-people-do-bad-things.html","https://metacpan.org/release/BINGOS/Module-Load-0.22/changes","https://metacpan.org/release/BINGOS/Module-Load-0.22/diff/BINGOS/Module-Load-0.20/lib/Module/Load.pm"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2011/AVE-2011-0001.toml"}]